AUTHORITATIVE JOIN RULES (MANDATORY):

Diagnoses are connected to claims ONLY through:
claims → service_summaries → service_summary_diagnosis → diagnoses

Services are connected ONLY through:
claims → claims_services → services

NEVER join diagnoses directly to claims.
NEVER join services directly to claims.
ALWAYS use the canonical join paths above.

❌ BAD EXAMPLE - DO NOT DO THIS:
Question: show diagnosis IDs with most cases
Bad SQL: SELECT diagnosis_id, COUNT(*) FROM service_summary_diagnosis GROUP BY diagnosis_id

✅ CORRECT APPROACH:
NEVER return diagnosis IDs. Always resolve to diagnoses.name and aggregate by claims.

❌ BAD EXAMPLE - DO NOT DO THIS:
Question: show diagnosis codes
Bad SQL: SELECT diagnosis_code, COUNT(*) FROM diagnoses GROUP BY diagnosis_code

✅ CORRECT APPROACH:
NEVER return diagnosis_code. Always use diagnoses.name for human-readable output.

❌ BAD EXAMPLE - DO NOT DO THIS:
Question: count service summaries
Bad SQL: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM service_summaries

✅ CORRECT APPROACH:
NEVER count service_summaries directly. Always count DISTINCT claims.id.

question_sql: "\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"which diagnosis had the most claims last year\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nWHERE YEAR(c.created_at) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE) - 1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nLIMIT 1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"phase1_gold_standard\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"most common diagnosis last year\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nWHERE YEAR(c.created_at) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE) - 1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nLIMIT 1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"phase1_common_diagnosis\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"diagnosis trends by month\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m') AS month,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS claim_count\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m')\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nORDER BY month DESC, claim_count DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"phase1_diagnosis_trends\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"average claim cost per diagnosis\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    AVG(c.total_cost) AS average_cost,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    SUM(c.total_cost) AS total_cost\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nORDER BY average_cost DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"phase1_cost_per_diagnosis\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"top diagnoses by service volume\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    s.description AS service,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(*) AS service_count\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN claims_services cs ON cs.claims_id = c.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJOIN services s ON s.id = cs.services_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, s.description\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nORDER BY service_count DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nLIMIT 20\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"phase1_diagnosis_service_volume\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"show me diseases with the highest number of patients\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                d.diagnosis_code,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                d.name as disease_name,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                COUNT(DISTINCT ss.id) as patient_count\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                FROM service_summaries ss\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                JOIN diagnoses d ON ss.diagnosis = d.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                WHERE d.diagnosis_code IS NOT NULL AND d.diagnosis_code != ''\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                GROUP BY d.diagnosis_code, d.name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                ORDER BY patient_count DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                LIMIT 100\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"diagnosis_aggregation\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"what is the disease with the highest number of patients\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                d.diagnosis_code,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                d.name as disease_name,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                COUNT(DISTINCT ss.id) as patient_count\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                FROM service_summaries ss\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                JOIN diagnoses d ON ss.diagnosis = d.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                WHERE d.diagnosis_code IS NOT NULL AND d.diagnosis_code != ''\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                GROUP BY d.diagnosis_code, d.name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                ORDER BY patient_count DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                LIMIT 1\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"diagnosis_top\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"\\\\\\\"{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"show me diagnosis codes with patient counts\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"SELECT \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                d.diagnosis_code,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                d.name as disease_name,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                COUNT(DISTINCT ss.id) as patient_count\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                FROM service_summaries ss\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                JOIN diagnoses d ON ss.diagnosis = d.id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                WHERE d.diagnosis_code IS NOT NULL AND d.diagnosis_code != ''\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                GROUP BY d.diagnosis_code, d.name\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                ORDER BY patient_count DESC\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"diagnosis_list\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}\\\\\\\"\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"most common diagnosis\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\\\\\\\nLIMIT 1\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern1_frequency\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"which diagnosis had the most claims last year\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nWHERE YEAR(c.created_at) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE) - 1\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\\\\\\\nLIMIT 1\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern1_frequency_time\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"top 10 diagnoses\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\\\\\\\nLIMIT 10\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern1_frequency_topn\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"diagnosis trend over time\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m') AS month,\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m')\\\\\\\\nORDER BY month DESC, total_claims DESC\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern2_trend\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"monthly diagnosis counts\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m') AS month,\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m')\\\\\\\\nORDER BY month DESC\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern2_trend_monthly\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"average claim cost per diagnosis\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    AVG(c.total_cost) AS avg_claim_cost\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nWHERE c.total_cost IS NOT NULL\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\nORDER BY avg_claim_cost DESC\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern3_cost\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"most expensive diagnosis\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    AVG(c.total_cost) AS avg_claim_cost,\\\\\\\\n    SUM(c.total_cost) AS total_cost\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nWHERE c.total_cost IS NOT NULL\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\\\\\nORDER BY avg_claim_cost DESC\\\\\\\\nLIMIT 1\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern3_cost_expensive\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"most common service per diagnosis\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    s.description AS service,\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(*) AS usage_count\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nJOIN claims_services cs ON cs.claims_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN services s ON s.id = cs.services_id\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, s.description\\\\\\\\nORDER BY usage_count DESC\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern4_service\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"\\\"{\\\\\\\"question\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"services used for diabetes\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"sql\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"SELECT\\\\\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\\\\\n    s.description AS service,\\\\\\\\n    COUNT(*) AS usage_count\\\\\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\\\\\nJOIN claims_services cs ON cs.claims_id = c.id\\\\\\\\nJOIN services s ON s.id = cs.services_id\\\\\\\\nWHERE d.name LIKE '%diabetes%'\\\\\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, s.description\\\\\\\\nORDER BY usage_count DESC\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"tag\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"phase2_pattern4_service_filtered\\\\\\\"}\\\"\""

"\"{\\\"question\\\": \\\"which diagnosis has the most claims\\\", \\\"sql\\\": \\\"SELECT\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\\\nLIMIT 1\\\", \\\"tag\\\": \\\"phase3_core1_most_common\\\"}\""

"\"{\\\"question\\\": \\\"show monthly trends of diagnoses\\\", \\\"sql\\\": \\\"SELECT\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\n    DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m') AS month,\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, month\\\\nORDER BY month\\\", \\\"tag\\\": \\\"phase3_core2_trend_monthly\\\"}\""

"\"{\\\"question\\\": \\\"what is the average claim cost per diagnosis\\\", \\\"sql\\\": \\\"SELECT\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\n    AVG(c.total_cost) AS avg_claim_cost\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\nWHERE c.total_cost IS NOT NULL\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\nORDER BY avg_claim_cost DESC\\\", \\\"tag\\\": \\\"phase3_core3_avg_cost\\\"}\""

"\"{\\\"question\\\": \\\"what services are most commonly used for each diagnosis\\\", \\\"sql\\\": \\\"SELECT\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\n    s.description AS service,\\\\n    COUNT(*) AS usage_count\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\nJOIN claims_services cs ON cs.claims_id = c.id\\\\nJOIN services s ON s.id = cs.services_id\\\\nGROUP BY d.name, s.description\\\\nORDER BY usage_count DESC\\\", \\\"tag\\\": \\\"phase3_core4_services_per_diagnosis\\\"}\""

"\"{\\\"question\\\": \\\"what were the top diagnoses last year\\\", \\\"sql\\\": \\\"SELECT\\\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\\\nFROM claims c\\\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\\\nWHERE YEAR(c.created_at) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE) - 1\\\\nGROUP BY d.name\\\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\\", \\\"tag\\\": \\\"phase3_core5_top_last_year\\\"}\""

"{\"question\": \"which diagnosis has the most claims\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\nFROM claims c\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\nGROUP BY d.name\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\\nLIMIT 1\", \"tag\": \"phase3_core1_most_common\"}"

"{\"question\": \"show monthly trends of diagnoses\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\n    DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m') AS month,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\nFROM claims c\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\nGROUP BY d.name, month\\nORDER BY month\", \"tag\": \"phase3_core2_trend_monthly\"}"

"{\"question\": \"what is the average claim cost per diagnosis\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\n    AVG(c.total_cost) AS avg_claim_cost\\nFROM claims c\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\nWHERE c.total_cost IS NOT NULL\\nGROUP BY d.name\\nORDER BY avg_claim_cost DESC\", \"tag\": \"phase3_core3_avg_cost\"}"

"{\"question\": \"what services are most commonly used for each diagnosis\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\n    s.description AS service,\\n    COUNT(*) AS usage_count\\nFROM claims c\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\nJOIN claims_services cs ON cs.claims_id = c.id\\nJOIN services s ON s.id = cs.services_id\\nGROUP BY d.name, s.description\\nORDER BY usage_count DESC\", \"tag\": \"phase3_core4_services_per_diagnosis\"}"

"{\"question\": \"show me the disease with highest number of patients\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    d.name AS disease,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS patient_count\\nFROM claims c\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\nGROUP BY d.name\\nORDER BY patient_count DESC\\nLIMIT 1\", \"tag\": \"phase3_core5_disease_most_patients\"}"

"{\"question\": \"what were the top diagnoses last year\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\nFROM claims c\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\nWHERE YEAR(c.created_at) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE) - 1\\nGROUP BY d.name\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\", \"tag\": \"phase3_core5_top_last_year\"}"

"{\"question\": \"which providers handled the most claims\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    p.provider_id AS provider,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\nFROM providers p\\nJOIN claims c ON c.provider_id = p.id\\nGROUP BY p.provider_id\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\", \"tag\": \"domain2_provider_volume\"}"

"{\"question\": \"what are the most common diagnoses per provider\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    p.provider_id AS provider,\\n    d.name AS diagnosis,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\nFROM providers p\\nJOIN claims c ON c.provider_id = p.id\\nJOIN service_summaries ss ON ss.claim_id = c.id\\nJOIN service_summary_diagnosis ssd ON ssd.service_summary_id = ss.id\\nJOIN diagnoses d ON d.id = ssd.diagnosis_id\\nGROUP BY p.provider_id, d.name\\nORDER BY total_claims DESC\", \"tag\": \"domain2_provider_diagnosis\"}"

"{\"question\": \"what services are most rendered by providers\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    p.provider_id AS provider,\\n    s.description AS service,\\n    COUNT(*) AS usage_count\\nFROM providers p\\nJOIN claims c ON c.provider_id = p.id\\nJOIN claims_services cs ON cs.claims_id = c.id\\nJOIN services s ON s.id = cs.services_id\\nGROUP BY p.provider_id, s.description\\nORDER BY usage_count DESC\", \"tag\": \"domain2_provider_service\"}"

"{\"question\": \"show monthly provider activity\", \"sql\": \"SELECT\\n    p.provider_id AS provider,\\n    DATE_FORMAT(c.created_at, '%Y-%m') AS month,\\n    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) AS total_claims\\nFROM providers p\\nJOIN claims c ON c.provider_id = p.id\\nGROUP BY p.provider_id, month\\nORDER BY month\", \"tag\": \"domain2_provider_trend\"}"

{"question": "what services are most rendered by providers", "sql": "SELECT
    p.provider_id AS provider,
    s.description AS service,
    COUNT(*) AS usage_count

JOIN claims c ON c.provider_id = p.id
